Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. At that point, I want to introduce Dr. Hawkins.\NOkay. Power to the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:01:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear a thumping. They're coming after me. Thump, thump. The thump, thumps almost got me,\Nbut they did not succeed because I have a will of iron. I iron my will all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.79,0:01:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, we're very serious about things this morning.\NWell, I've greeted the people in my usual style of absurdity, which is the only sanity left.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.26,0:01:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Absurdity is the only sanity left to mankind. So we're going to answer any questions people\Nmay have this morning. Is that what we're doing? I read that. You want to read that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.65,0:02:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I thank you for your infinite love beyond the time and space.\NHe has to be closer to the mic. A little bit closer to the mic, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We came from Korea. We came from Korea, South Korea. We have gone through a hard time\Nto get permission to come here. They had a hard time getting permission to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.30,0:02:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Because I am an army officer. Because what? He's an army officer.\NOh, yeah. To come here, I have to obtain permission from my four bosses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.74,0:02:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It is so difficult and a complicated process. I intensely aspire.\NHe's got to be closer to the mic. It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.96,0:03:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I intensely aspire to attend. He's got to be closer to the mic, please. Your mouth.\NGood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NWhat did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very difficult for him to come from Korea because he has four different bosses,\Nbasically, to get permission from.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:04:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NSo he is thankful that he's able to get permission to come this time as well as he
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.96,0:04:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,wants to know if it's in the highest good that he come, if possible, to come here.\NHe wants to know what's in the highest good?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.90,0:04:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If it serves the highest good for him to come here.\NIs that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.17,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little late to ask that, isn't it?\NWell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he ...\NMy asking is prayer, your prayer for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.57,0:04:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants you to pray for him to be able to come.\NTo continue to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To continue to come here.\NIt's in his own highest good to be here, Jesus. And we pray for his welfare, O Lord. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to come here.\NWe want to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.14,0:04:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We want to come here.\NWe want to come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We went to Korea, Susan and I, some years ago.\NWas it once or twice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Twice.\NWe went to Korea twice, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,And it takes too long to fly there now.\NThey were going to have supersonic jets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.10,0:05:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, they never got around to the supersonic jets.\NBut I thought if they got around to supersonic jets,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.66,0:05:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,we would fly there again.\NAnd we had a wonderful time in Korea, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we loved the country.\NI know right now that Korean is under great stress
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,as far as it goes with North Korea,\Nso we appreciate very much that you were able to come to this panel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.00,0:05:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a gift from me and my wife.\NNext questioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.54,0:05:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you take a picture with us?\NWell, thank you for coming all the way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:06:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,All the way from North Korea to be here.\NThey're the Koreans, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.16,0:06:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.23,0:06:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we flew twice to Korea.\NMet with a lot of government people.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, she's going to read one, too.\NThey already, because they speak very little English...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, oh, oh.\NI see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't speak much Korean, either.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Recently,\NI have,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,intensely prayed to dear Lord\Nto make me an instrument of the Lord
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.19,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and surrender my life,\Nmy being,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and my existence.\NBut when I pray to God,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.79,0:07:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,your image comes to mind,\Nthen I can't differentiate God from you
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,to whom I pray.\NYour energy is closer to me
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,than even Jesus Christ.\NYour voice rings in my ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And I am anxious without your picture in my sight.\NI devote my time to listen to your DVDs
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and read your books as much as possible.\NIs it okay that I cherish you in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.39,0:07:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as God's image,\Nor am I idol-worshipping?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.\NWhat did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.36,0:08:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What'd she say, huh?\NWell, she...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it's because,\Nyou know,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.05,0:08:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,God and Doc are totally separate,\Nbut his message is
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a combination of\Nself-realization of your own spiritual worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.66,0:08:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So, basically,\Nthe messages are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThe messages are all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What messages?\NI don't know what he's talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.42,0:08:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NWell, you go ahead and answer it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer it?\NI don't know what the question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, she said she listens to your DVDs every day.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And she cannot distinguish between you and God.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.30,0:09:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And is she idol-worshipping?\NWell, God really speaks to all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.69,0:09:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's only a matter of learning how to listen.\NGod speaks to all of us, all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we learn how to listen.\NWe walk through the woods,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.05,0:09:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,and we hear the birds singing.\NAnd if you're naive, you don't realize
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.29,0:09:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,that's God singing to you via the bird.\NEverything that presents itself to you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is divinity,\Nbecause nothing else but divinity exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.37,0:09:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NAll that exists is divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.86,0:10:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing else exists.\NTherefore, you don't have to worry about finding God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.75,0:10:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,God's everywhere.\NWhat you have to come to is the realization
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,that the essence of everything that exists is divinity.\NNothing exists except God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.90,0:10:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, we treat everything in life with respect.\NWe treat everything and everyone with respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.60,0:10:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,because everyone and everything reflects\Ndivinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.02,0:10:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Other than God, what could there be?\NNon-God?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.49,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NThis is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.60,0:10:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is God.\NThis is God.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.62,0:10:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is not God.\NHa, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.62,0:10:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NHa, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.70,0:10:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NHa, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming up.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:11:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Blessing for my spiritual pathway.\NBless for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you want to test?\NBless.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.87,0:11:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she wants a blessing.\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.45,0:11:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She wants a blessing.\NNo, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.45,0:11:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NHa, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.45,0:11:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you, sweetheart.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NGod bless your courage for coming up in front of the audience
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and speaking to us all.\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:30.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming here.\NMay I hold your hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.12,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?\NHa, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now she wants a lollipop.\NYou want a lollipop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a lollipop?\NHa, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NHa, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.29,0:11:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NYou want a lollipop?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.29,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You want dessert on top of it?\NWhat do you want now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NOh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NAll right, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very brave to come up in front of a whole audience.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.19,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.37,0:12:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a question, and I just wanted to meet you and to come up and to say thank\Nyou for being a light in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.74,0:12:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't understand what this microphone said.\NWhat did she just say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.53,0:12:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She just wants to thank you.\NThank you for being here in the world with the work that you're doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I didn't have much to say about it.\NGod said, you're going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.16,0:12:34.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, okay, boss.\NHa, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.16,0:12:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We incarnate when divinity wills it, when it's God's will for us to become a human again,\Nand we do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.35,0:13:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NAnd in the world of the physical expression, when we're done with that, we retreat back
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to the world of spirit, and then maybe reemerge later again in the world of the physical.\NSo it's up to God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.83,0:13:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.50,0:13:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't obey God's will, uh-oh, you're in trouble.\NMm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha.\NAnd can I have a blessing from you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.83,0:13:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.14,0:13:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.91,0:13:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:14:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is in regards to prayer.\NIn one of your lectures, you talk about clearing things using intense prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering how one makes their prayers intense or how you make your prayers intense?\NI don't understand the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, you talked about a clearing prayer, you know.\NOh, a clearing prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.\NAnd so...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.53,0:14:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you can minimize, I guess, through extensive prayer.\NSo he says, how do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Intense prayer.\NIntense prayer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you do that?\NThe clearing prayer, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, when you say that you're intensely praying,\Nhow is that different than a regular prayer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NIt's not really different.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:15:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a degree of intensity.\NI don't know how to explain to people intensity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The amount of energy and power that you give it,\Nand you invoke it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you invoke it in God's name,\Nin the name of the Father, the Son, and the Holy Spirit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.99,0:15:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,now and forever, amen,\Nthen you are invoking it very, very strongly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.62,0:15:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,And the intensity of your devotion\Nand
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,the level of one's own personal energy tends to increase it.\NTo pray intensely, in a way, redoubles it,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.00,0:15:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,because in a way, all you're doing is reflecting back to God\Nthat which is divinity in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.70,0:16:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,which is manifesting as your existence.\NBut you don't have to figure that out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.10,0:16:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NI just want to first express my great gratitude to you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.80,0:16:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had...\Na lot of serenity since I've been coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with a potential university...\Nmy potential university education.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your potential university education?\NCorrect.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYou state that a true liberal education
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.36,0:16:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,is the great books of the Western world.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.77,0:17:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You said that the great books of the Western world\Nis what you read when you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThat would be the equivalent of going to college, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.15,0:17:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been accepted into a program\Nwhere the curriculum is great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.91,0:17:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes.\NAt a small college.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.32,0:17:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I forget the name of that college.\NWhat's the name of the college?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's St. John's College.\NYeah, St. John's.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.\NTheir curriculum is the great books of the Western world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.76,0:17:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Great books of the Western world.\NI remember calibrating it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A calibrator is quite high, I guess.\NYeah, I guess that's my question is
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.58,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,you speak extensively in your lectures\Nand books about the fall of academia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.45,0:17:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?\NAbout what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.48,0:17:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Something about academia.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You've spoken extensively about the...\Nthe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.43,0:18:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,lack of integrity in academia in today's world.\NAnd I guess my question is I feel drawn to this study
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.38,0:18:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,and I guess I'm not...\NI'd like to know if the integrity of the program is still intact.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.99,0:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,At St. John's?\NAt St. John's, that's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he wants to know if it's still...\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.75,0:18:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The integrity...\NWe have permission to ask this about St. John's.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.80,0:18:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The integrity of their curriculum is still intact.\NThey follow the great books of the Western world, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.74,0:19:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.27,0:19:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It calibrates higher than Harvard.\NIt calibrates higher than Harvard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.02,0:19:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That should be good enough.\NNot that Harvard calibrates all that high, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.17,0:19:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Harvard's got the name,\Nbut this other college has the integrity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.71,0:19:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NYes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.23,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.\NGood morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.47,0:19:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,In healing and recovery,\Nyou have a chapter on death and dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.40,0:19:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And you describe one can use their imagination\Nto help those close to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.29,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,For instance, someone in the battlefield\Nor even yesterday in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.38,0:20:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you clarify how to do this process\Nif you don't know anyone specifically
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,that you would be using your imagination?\NIn behalf of the people who are praying for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan's full of people.\NPeople are praying for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.39,0:20:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And so you try to reinforce it\Nby collaborating with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.50,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,adding the energy of your own psyche\Nto their intention
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to increase the effectiveness of their prayer.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NIt's like you're praying in their behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.38,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In their behalf.\NSo you don't have to be specific.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NYou can if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.16,0:20:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you don't know an individual,\NI don't know any individuals in Japan right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can pray on behalf of those who are suffering\Nand threatened for their peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.58,0:21:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.03,0:21:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hawkins, my question is several years ago,\NI was in, I had a rebirthing session.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.28,0:21:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NAnd I thought I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NI thought I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a question.\NWhat is your question?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:30.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to ask.\NYou don't have to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to ask.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.84,0:21:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to ask.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.84,0:21:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NBut I had a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.84,0:21:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NAnd my heart opened up like a flower so slowly.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.41,0:21:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I felt absolute, undescribable total peace.\NYou felt what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Peace.\NPeace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.52,0:21:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yes.\NTotal peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.52,0:21:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Indescribable peace.\NYes, yes, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.52,0:21:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a profound peace.\NAll over my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.52,0:21:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Completely.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And it was residual.\NIt lasted for several months.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.52,0:22:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was just wondering if I could have that calibrated?\NWould that be okay?
