Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.52,0:22:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That, that event.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did she have that event calibrated that she had?\NThat spiritual experience that I had.
