Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.40,0:22:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a very high level of love, yes.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.90,0:22:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of like a peak at what could be.\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.18,0:22:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, right.\NDid you re-experience your own birth?
