Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.26,0:39:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,teacher who calibrates under 500 we have permission to ask this the answer is yes the answer is yes\Nokay yeah thank you very much i appreciate it it doesn't mean that he's enlightened but
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.21,0:39:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,right you could learn from his teaching exactly right okay yeah that's the reason people go\Nit's the reason people go to church it doesn't mean that the priest has to become
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.46,0:39:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you know calibrated a thousand the same as jesus christ right that wouldn't be my expectation yeah\Nokay and but for zen buddhists to follow zen buddhist practice to help me along the path
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.34,0:39:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,okay thank you very much appreciate it at one time or another just about everybody's useful along the\Npath you know what i mean my question is about parents i'm kind of curious if before we incarnate
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.71,0:40:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,on this life do we pick our parents or our family for the highest karmic undoing um when we come\Nbefore we come back into this life do we pick our parents for the highest karmic learning i don't
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.23,0:40:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,know i don't know\NDo we pick our parents?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.44,0:40:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, we have permission to ask this.\NWe do have a say in picking our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.42,0:40:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And the spiritual levels are very determining.\NYep.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.17,0:40:26.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.82,0:40:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That undoes a lot.\NI have very spiritually committed parents, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.88,0:40:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Extremely, very intense.\NWe went to church every Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.32,0:40:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Boy, oh boy.\NAnd we didn't eat any meat during Lent.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.92,0:40:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Much less on Good Friday.\NIf you ate meat on Good Friday, you'd probably go to hell, I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.07,0:41:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NI've had many high experiences in my lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.80,0:41:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of miracles.\NWonderful things.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.96,0:41:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Had abusive parents.\NIronic on that last question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.17,0:41:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Physically.\NAnd emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.15,0:41:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ended up marrying a woman much like an emotional abusive mother.\NMuch like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.96,0:41:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The emotional abusive mother that he had.\NOh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.48,0:41:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is that?\NBut anyhow, it's not my question.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.92,0:41:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Emotionally abusive?\NYou stupid idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.69,0:41:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.90,0:41:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the deal?\NWhat a dumb guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.88,0:41:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It was familiar.\NI guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.94,0:41:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.36,0:41:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That ended up in divorce.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.42,0:42:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay.\NOkay, so the propensity is that I got in trouble a lot as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.17,0:42:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I always had that feeling of going to the principal's office in the pit of my stomach.\NAnd it seems such a paradox to have really high experiences and a wonderful relationship with divinity.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.84,0:42:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And then all of a sudden, you just feel in your gut that...\NYou know, here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.84,0:42:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding this is certainly ego attachments.\NBut I just can't figure out how to unlock it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.69,0:42:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,How to...\NI surrendered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.26,0:42:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm missing something.\NI guess that other people have hurt me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.00,0:43:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I guess it's starting to come clear that am I angry at myself for walking into this situation and allowing...\NThings...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.07,0:43:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a mystery still to me.\NI don't quite understand it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.80,0:43:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't understand what?\NI don't get what the question is.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.63,0:43:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NYour life gets screwed up periodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.53,0:43:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That occurred...\NThat applies to everybody on the planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.03,0:43:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.19,0:43:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,For what is it?\NFor me?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.21,0:43:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.92,0:43:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I...\NI...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.44,0:43:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I knew what I was going to ask you when I was over here.\NAnd I'm really confused right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.84,0:43:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.\NI think that's part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.15,0:43:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Always...\NFearful of...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.28,0:43:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of getting everybody's approval.\NYou know, rather than just standing up for the...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.05,0:43:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.94,0:43:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm completely confused.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.28,0:43:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The minute you bring a third party in, you're adding to the confusion.\NTheir opinion, their attitude, their approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.03,0:43:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NSo you have to let go wanting other people's approval in order to get your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.80,0:43:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that so?\NAs long as you're wanting everybody...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.80,0:44:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody's approval, then you haven't achieved your own.\NWhen you become independent of other people's opinions, it doesn't mean to become ignorant
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.69,0:44:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,of them.\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.69,0:44:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of people become clumsy and stupid, and it'd be better that they stayed in bed\Nall day.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.11,0:44:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.11,0:44:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.11,0:44:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, you need to forgive.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.11,0:44:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Because...\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.11,0:44:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They were...\NDoing their best.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.11,0:44:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know that they were even doing their best, but you have to forgive them for\Nwhat took place.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.11,0:44:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.55,0:44:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.48,0:44:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're trying to soft-soap it, but it wasn't.\NI mean, if they really did...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.26,0:44:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You really were miserable, then they weren't doing their best.\NYou don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.03,0:44:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So you need to just forgive them and put it in the past and realize that you're destined\Nfor other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.19,0:44:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NIn the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.32,0:45:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,But you have to let go of that, because that's holding you down.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.36,0:45:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Every now and then, there's an occasional zinger.\NJust a couple months ago, my mom threw a grenade in my lap, and she's so disappointed at the
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.57,0:45:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,way I turned out.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.21,0:45:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,His mom threw a grenade in his lap, because she was disappointed on the way he turned\Nout.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.55,0:45:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A grenade?\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.57,0:45:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you need to forgive him and walk away.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.21,0:45:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I moved.\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.21,0:45:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NI would, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.21,0:45:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fast.\NDo you want to get a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.21,0:45:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NWell, it's nice if your mother can be proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.21,0:45:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so wonderful.\NI always worked for my mother's approval.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.38,0:45:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I always got her approval, because...\NI did what she approved of.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.00,0:45:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It makes it simple.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.00,0:45:56.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NGood morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.86,0:46:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NDr. Hawkins, thank you very much for being here with us today.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.07,0:46:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I have recently been dealing with a sarcoma cancer issue.\NYou got to speak slowly, and then the mic.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.48,0:46:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You recently have what?\NI have recently been dealing with a sarcoma cancer issue.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.50,0:46:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A cancer issue.\NShe what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.46,0:46:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...\NShe's been dealing with cancer.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.46,0:46:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\Nso I have accepted that
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.94,0:46:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,as my karma\NI have accepted that as my karma
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.36,0:46:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand from your teachings\Nthat at some level
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.32,0:46:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I may have attracted this to me\NI understand from your teachings
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.09,0:46:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that I may have attracted this to me\Nwell attraction is not exactly the right word
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.05,0:47:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,created it\Noccasioned it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.03,0:47:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,so getting any kind of an illness\Ncould have a karmic antecedent
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.19,0:47:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,that is true\Nso if that is true
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.57,0:47:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,from now on\Nhow does one not attract illness to them
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.76,0:47:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it is not the right wording attract\Nyou make it sound like a bug flying around
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.80,0:47:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,and you attract the bug\Nand you attract the bug
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.57,0:47:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,and you attract the bug\Nand he lands on your arm
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.71,0:47:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,how do you avoid the consequences\Nof having bad karma
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.59,0:47:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is really what she is saying\Nwell what you do is
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.80,0:47:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to create as much good\Nkarma for yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.40,0:47:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can to counterbalance it\Nyou try to counterbalance it
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.98,0:47:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to compensate for it\Nby as much
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.69,0:48:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritual evolution\Nas you can
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.42,0:48:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,accomplish\Nand the rest is up to God
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.80,0:48:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,you know\Nyes thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.86,0:48:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you very much\NI would like a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.84,0:48:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and stay out of trouble\NI don't have a question
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.42,0:48:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to say thank you\Nand I also have a gift for you
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.42,0:49:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nthank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.76,0:49:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a desire to meet you\Nand to be close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.76,0:49:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and I am thankful for God that I\NI am thankful for God that I am here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.84,0:49:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have had that opportunity today\Nand I just ask your blessings on my life
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.90,0:49:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,he just wanted to meet you\Nand ask your blessings
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.13,0:49:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,on opening the heart\Nand your blessings on opening
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.13,0:49:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the heart up\Noh God bless you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.13,0:49:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\Nkaboom
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.23,0:49:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,can I shake your hand?\Nsure come over here
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.23,0:49:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,now he wants my hand\Ngood God what else?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.05,0:49:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you\NThank you guys for your dedication and willingness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.59,0:50:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from China.\NRight now the government lacks transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.98,0:50:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now what?\NThe government lacks transparency.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.17,0:50:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Transparency and-\NIn China?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.38,0:50:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.38,0:50:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Integrity.\NAnd the media is blocked and controlled by the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.07,0:50:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So democracy is a really big issue there, and it's influencing all the people.\NSo my question is, as a citizen and simply a human being, what can I do to improve the
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.78,0:50:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,situation?\NImprove the situation where?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.05,0:50:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In China, because they're blocking all the media and the internet, they only allow certain\Nthings to come into China, and it has to do with the politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.84,0:50:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a person-\NHas to do with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.84,0:50:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it has to do with the politics.\NThe politics of the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.80,0:50:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The climate.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.80,0:51:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.\NSo as an individual, what could he do that would change this situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.94,0:51:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't advise trying to change it.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.98,0:51:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not unless you're willing to die soon.\NAre you?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.71,0:51:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NNot right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.71,0:51:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was the emperor of China and you came to me with that, I would ask them to remove\Nyour head promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.05,0:51:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a disrespect for authority.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.36,0:51:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,See, in a certain culture, authority necessitates respect, and it's not up to you to decide\Nwho deserves it, who deserves respect.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.19,0:51:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not up to you.\NThe king is the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.73,0:51:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if he's a bad king, he's still the king.\NSo the sovereign is still the sovereign.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.01,0:51:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So you have to respect the position of the sovereign and ignore the personality.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.17,0:52:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Many of the great kings of history were terrible people.\NBut they were still king, whether you liked it or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.40,0:52:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So ...\NSo we cannot pick or choose.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.65,0:52:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that this could be turned around by prayer, or ...\NWhat turned around?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.80,0:52:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the situation that the government is blocking all outside information ...\NNo, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.15,0:52:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So he just has to know that this is the way it is, and that's it?\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.09,0:52:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way it is.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:27.09,0:52:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But people will ... democracy will still be insufficient in China, keep being like that?\NIt might change, but it's going to take a while before China gets caught up with the
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.34,0:52:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,rest of the world.\NIt might change tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.65,0:52:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know.\NBut ...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.65,0:52:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, all kinds of situations change.\NYou get idealistic about how a country should behave.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.63,0:52:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you do about overpopulation?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.73,0:52:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NPass a law.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.86,0:53:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up sex.\NNo more babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.86,0:53:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,China allows you one baby, huh?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:03.86,0:53:05.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're allowed one baby.\NBut if I marry a single child from the family, I'm allowed to have two.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.86,0:53:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.86,0:53:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So I read your book, The Truth Versus Falsehood.\NIn that book, you ... the China ... Chinese government is calibrated in 190, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.86,0:53:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is ...\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.86,0:53:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.86,0:53:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.86,0:53:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.86,0:53:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.86,0:53:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.86,0:53:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.86,0:53:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.86,0:53:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.86,0:53:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:29.86,0:53:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time.\NAt that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:31.86,0:53:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time.\NAt that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.86,0:53:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you calibrate right now the Chinese government?\NRight now, Chinese government ... We have permission to do Chinese government
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.82,0:53:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,right now.\NIt's over 190, 195, 200, 199, 198, 195.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.63,0:53:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Chinese government has come up.\NIt's coming up?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.73,0:53:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NIt is still growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.73,0:54:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still ... Yeah.\NSo it is looking like it is going towards change.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.69,0:54:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's just gonna take a while.\Nbut it's just going to take a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.86,0:54:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a citizen, I can only accept the fact.\NThat's your opinion. That's your advice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.34,0:54:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, China has been like it has been for many, many, many, many years.\NAnd the world around it has changed, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.09,0:54:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,while China still remains as it was.\NSo it'll take a while before the change will come up and take over,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.67,0:54:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but it will eventually come.\NWell, you see, in a democracy,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.51,0:54:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the head of the country changes all the time.\NThis person's here for four years,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.15,0:54:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,then he goes out and somebody else comes in.\NIt's constantly changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.71,0:54:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NTrying to think what the politics were in China when I was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.21,0:54:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in China a couple of times\Ntrying to remember what the politics was at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.19,0:55:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, you can't have more than one child, yes?\NUnless you marry someone that's a single.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.42,0:55:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,A single child, yeah.\NUh-huh, uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.28,0:55:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you know, the rulers do what they can with the situation,\Nand then when the situation changes, they must change, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.80,0:55:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So as a citizen, I just await the situation change?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.69,0:55:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You can talk about it, but, yeah, you have to wait for it to change.\NOkay. Thank you, Doctor. Thank you, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.28,0:55:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved China when I was there.\NI loved the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.30,0:55:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NOkay, let's do one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:44.80,0:55:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, great food, too.\NAll the restaurants were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.98,0:55:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.23,0:56:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you and ask for a blessing.\NWhat did he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.71,0:56:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He wants to ask for a blessing.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:09.46,0:56:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you.\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.11,0:56:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What else?\NI have a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.76,0:56:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NYou have a question?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.96,0:56:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I have a question.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.44,0:56:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,If you could please expand on fulfilling your potential a little bit,\Nbecause I am confused sometimes between working too much as a part of my function here
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.36,0:56:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and wasting time for spiritual progress.\NHe wants you to talk about one's potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.15,0:57:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He feels like he devotes a lot of time to...\Nto work, and that, you know, there's...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.67,0:57:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,All of us do that, and there's very little time left over for spiritual work.\NOh.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.92,0:57:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the balance, you know, sometimes we just...\NWell, that's the wrong way of looking at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.94,0:57:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.46,0:57:35.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Spiritual is an inner attitude, and nothing can interrupt it.\NIt has nothing to do with work, because to be in a certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.42,0:57:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,attitude or way with life, it doesn't depend on what's going on out there.\NTo be appreciative of life in all of its expressions,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.98,0:57:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,to be grateful for life in all of its expressions,\Ndoes not put any requirements on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.26,0:58:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It puts the requirement on you.\NYou have to be happy whether it's raining or whether the sun is shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.17,0:58:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say, well, I'm only going to be happy when the sun shines.\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.03,0:58:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You begin to see that all the weather is fun.\NIf it's a rainy day this morning, you say, well, wow, it's raining today.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.13,0:58:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's sunny, you say, oh, wow, it's a sunny day.\NIf it's snowing, you say, hey, look, it's snowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.80,0:58:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what I'm saying?\NHello?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.21,0:58:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he home?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.69,0:58:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NThis week, a week ago, we had a very exciting morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.23,0:58:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We got up, and Susan said, it's snowing outside.\NYay!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.36,0:58:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I jump all over the place.\NIf you live in Arizona, if it's snowing, it's a big day.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.03,0:59:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If you live in New York, snowing is not a big day.\NSo context decides the significance and meaning of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.07,0:59:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just snow?\NNo, it's snow where and when and under what circumstance.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.00,0:59:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you've had a whole winter of snow,\Nthe fact that it's snowing today is not exactly good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.59,0:59:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's what I mean by context.\NSo the significance of many things in our life,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.11,0:59:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,you know, very dependent on context to whom it's happening and when\Nand in what kind of a situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.55,0:59:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,As a woman will say, to be pregnant at a certain time and month in her life was fantastic.\NIf it had happened under different circumstances, she'd think of suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.11,0:59:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.21,0:59:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NCan I have a picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.94,0:59:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.94,1:00:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So circumstances contribute to the meaning, yeah?\NOkay, we're going to take a quick break, about 15 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.90,1:00:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and then we'll come back and finish questions.\NBum-pa-bum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.88,1:00:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum-pa-bum-pum.\NTry to get them to say bum-pa-bum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.88,1:00:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Bum-pa-bum-pum.\NOur bird says bum-pa-bum-pum.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.51,1:00:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,All the police, I think I'm being kidnapped.\NOh, God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.01,1:00:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all for being here.\NI give thanks for their presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.92,1:01:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.\NOh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.36,1:01:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to thank you for beautiful work, and you.\NI was in Thailand at a monastery for about 150 days, where I want to reach enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.25,1:01:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to speak slower and right into the mic.\NYou were in Thailand?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.36,1:01:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In an Indiana Buddhist center, monastery, where I want to reach enlightenment.\NBut I had difficulties with negative.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:45.61,1:01:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not hearing them.\NDifficulties with negative energy.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.32,1:01:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.\NWhat does he mean by negative entities?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.19,1:02:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Negative thoughts or what?\NYeah, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.30,1:02:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It comes true, and then I couldn't do my thing.\NLike, I really want to go to reach enlightenment, but it threw my mind, and I didn't reach.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.38,1:02:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NSo do you have any?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:20.80,1:02:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any, I don't know, answer for it, or?\NHe really felt like he applied himself to reach enlightenment, but it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.34,1:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't reach it, so is there any?\NWhat did he think he was going to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.01,1:02:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Get enlightened between Monday and Friday, or what?\NYou got another 50 years to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.09,1:02:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NNo, what you do is you state your intention.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.63,1:02:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NAnd then you surrender it to God.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.38,1:02:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't keep trying to control it.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:58.42,1:03:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,When you ask God to reach enlightenment, it's now up to God, not up to you.\NAnd if it's slated to happen, then it will happen, and nothing can stop it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.71,1:03:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not slated to happen.\NNothing will make it happen.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.07,1:03:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NExcept that you will end up at death as a frustrated devotee.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.75,1:03:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NWell, you have to have some kind of karma in the next lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.36,1:03:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So to die in this lifetime, a frustrated devotee.\NProbably would have a very good God will feel sorry for you, and you get reborn in Zen Monastery or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.07,1:03:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NSo don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.19,1:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering it to God means surrendering it to God.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.94,1:04:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're meant to be enlightened, then it will come about no matter what.\NIt requires several things.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:04.25,1:04:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,One is karmic propensity, infinite divine mercy, and many other things.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.92,1:04:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And many other factors of which we do not know.\NWhen it comes on, it is very sudden and very unexpected and very profound, profoundly changes
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.80,1:04:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,everything.\NWhat everything looks like, what it seems to be, what its reality is, all changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:40.80,1:04:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NAnd once it's changed, so you can see from a changed viewpoint, then you're not being
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.21,1:04:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,frustrated.\NAll right?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.00,1:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NWhat about being frustrated?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.00,1:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,May I take a picture?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:59.07,1:05:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NBeing frustrated means that you're, you know, not surrendering to God's will.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.98,1:05:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,God's will is things happen by karmic propensities, plus God's will, plus many circumstances of\Nwhich we have no awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:06.15,1:05:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NI think it's the willingness that counts more than anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.86,1:05:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:10.86,1:05:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:18.03,1:05:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.03,1:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.71,1:05:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.71,1:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.84,1:05:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.03,1:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.76,1:05:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.76,1:05:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.71,1:05:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Namaste.\NDr. Hawkins, I'm very blessed to be in your presence.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.23,1:06:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I was told six months ago that I would meet my teacher that I have studied with in past\Nlives, and I knew it was you, and I'm very blessed that you are here in my life and in
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.19,1:06:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,everyone's life.\NI appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.40,1:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask what's on my mind.\NI am that teacher. Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:24.82,1:06:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what do you know?\NYou look familiar from a couple thousand years ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.57,1:06:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember you from Fum Boo, the year 2012.\NOkay, no, I'm glad you've returned.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.61,1:06:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.50,1:06:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My question is about choiceless awareness.\NChoices and awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:58.92,1:07:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Choiceless.\NChoiceless awareness.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.19,1:07:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Choiceless awareness. What does that mean?\NThat means once you're in that state of presence,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.05,1:07:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,when you are so imbued in the presence of presence,\Nthat there's no choiceless.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:14.19,1:07:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything just flows and just happens.\NAnd you've spoken so beautifully about it many, many times.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:20.69,1:07:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When you're in that state...\NYou're always in that state.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:25.53,1:07:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always in that state.\NSo where does...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.65,1:07:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I realize it.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.01,1:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NEverything is flowing perfectly with ultimate beauty,
Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.71,1:07:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and perfection right now.\NIt's obvious, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.17,1:07:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's obvious.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.32,1:07:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So where does choice fit in then?\NOh, that was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.55,1:08:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I go back and forth with just being in that choiceless state,\Nand then the dualistic choice kicks in.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.90,1:08:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, there's what you're thinking about at the moment.\NThen there's what your life is really about.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.07,1:08:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So we don't think every moment about what our life is really about,\Nbecause you'd never get a chance to live it.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.09,1:08:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You spend all your time thinking about it.\NSo we make our choice, you know, to visit China, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.35,1:08:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that only takes one second to make the choice.\NYou don't have to think about it on the plane all the way to China,
Dialogue: 0,1:08:35.10,1:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you know what I'm saying?\NI'm choosing to go to China and say, repeat that over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.96,1:08:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've already made a choice,\Nand it's sent your life in this direction rather than this direction, see?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.15,1:08:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So don't worry about it.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.80,1:09:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless you're overcome by evil, your life is fine.\NGod bless you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.93,1:09:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There'll be a hand on you.\NOh, now it's official.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.69,1:09:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, she could be right and I could be wrong, you know what I'm saying?\NGet to heaven, and God says,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.36,1:09:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,how come you didn't put your hand on that lady's head?\NSend me back to Chicago for a lifer.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.18,1:09:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, go ahead.\NGood morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.27,1:09:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NFirst of all, I want to give you a copy of my master's thesis in divinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.55,1:09:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,where I extensively cited your work.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:40.86,1:09:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brilliant work.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.78,1:09:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,And I would like to ask you if you would please calibrate it.\NCalibrate the work?
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.22,1:09:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Calibrate it.\NOkay, I have permission to calibrate the thesis.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.84,1:09:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over 450, 470, 480, 490.\N500.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:59.73,1:10:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's right at 500.\NWow, that's great.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.61,1:10:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very good.\NThat's excellent.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:12.42,1:10:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could ask for more?\NPretty good, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.07,1:10:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NI'm very grateful to be here, and thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.39,1:10:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a question about the value of perseverance.\NIn my work, I have a company that's developing small airplanes, small jets,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.28,1:10:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,and it appears to be.\NI'm financially failing, and I have a dilemma of how to know when to move on to something else,
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.82,1:10:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,or what the value of it is.\NYou have a choice?
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.72,1:10:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't be in too bad shape if you've got a choice.\NWell, having a choice is a blessing, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.76,1:11:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What is the choice about?\NWell, to persevere with it indefinitely, or to let go and move on.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.10,1:11:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see what you mean, yeah.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:07.10,1:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NOther ventures and other things.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.11,1:11:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to ask the arm?\NI would appreciate that very much, sure.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:13.85,1:11:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be in his, I have permission to ask this.\NIt would be in his best interest to persevere with this.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.13,1:11:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.\NCould he resume it at a different date?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.05,1:11:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it may be the wrong time, the wrong company, the wrong financing.\NIt could be a thousand factors.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.85,1:11:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Could maybe at a later date?\NOh, should he be, it might be appropriate to return to the same endeavor at a later date.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.92,1:11:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or is this, oh, okay.\NI just got that.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.38,1:11:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, well, you got it, yeah.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.07,1:11:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate it very much.\NMay I take your hands?
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.26,1:11:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.14,1:11:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the timing may be off.\NGood luck.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:54.40,1:12:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:07.06,1:12:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NI gave up wanting things from God for Lent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:13.78,1:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NShe gave up wanting things from God for Lent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:18.22,1:12:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanting things from God?\NFor Lent.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.90,1:12:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for Lent.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.90,1:12:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.\NGee, what if you got them anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.19,1:12:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?\NWell, instead of, well, I'm praying for God's will instead of praying for what.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:40.48,1:12:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see what you mean, yes.\NI want his will for me.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.14,1:12:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThat's fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.01,1:12:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and when I pray in the morning, when I pray in the morning, I pray what is thy will,\Nand how can I?
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.03,1:12:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I be your servant today?\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.97,1:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And most often, I just, it's silence.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.85,1:13:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And I don't know how to know which way to proceed.\NMy husband said, if you surrender to every moment,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:17.32,1:13:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\Nthen that's being in God's will.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.51,1:13:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.75,1:13:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.\NWhatever is, is, and we have to assume,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.06,1:13:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that divinity is the source.\NWithout divinity, you and I wouldn't be speaking here at this table,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.57,1:13:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,nor would Susan be sitting here, you understand?\NSo the whole phenomena is a product of multiple composites.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.28,1:13:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.\NAnd we add our two cents worth in at the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.19,1:14:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And let it be a blue Cadillac, Lord.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.84,1:14:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NAll I want is a mercer to these bands.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.98,1:14:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I sat next to her one time in an auditorium.\NShe was on that day.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.85,1:14:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Janice Joplin.\NThat's who it was.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.36,1:14:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't think of her name.\NI'm so happy to be here.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.93,1:14:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm going to ask a question for my dear friend from Seattle.\NShe was wondering, and her name is Pam,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.30,1:14:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,how lower astral entities,\Nare they actually part of God, too,
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.92,1:15:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,with having non-duality?\NAre they God, too?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:06.67,1:15:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\NAre lower astral entities God, as well?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.56,1:15:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Is God in them?\NThey're godless.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.18,1:15:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they're lower astral.\NThey're godless.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.39,1:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they're lower astral.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.11,1:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NHow does that fit with non-duality?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.98,1:15:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How does that fit?\NHow does that fit with non-duality?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.72,1:15:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what it's got to do with non-duality.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.06,1:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.36,1:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the denial of God and divine attributes\Nis what gets you to the lower astral.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.35,1:16:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Avoid love, choose hate,\Nchoose revenge instead of forgiveness.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.25,1:16:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you get to hell.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.23,1:16:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell something's evil when they think hell is a great place.\NI'm stomping.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:17.43,1:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The stomper is here.\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:21.11,1:16:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just having fun with you.\NI want to thank you for your essences
Dialogue: 0,1:16:25.96,1:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and your wonderful gifts of your books and your being.\NAnd I have a question.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:32.10,1:16:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I talked to you about seven years ago,\Nand you helped me a lot at that time.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.65,1:16:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And my question now is I had an experience where I was meditating,\Nand there were two triangles that intersected into my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.73,1:16:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and made the shape of the sign of Solomon.\NOr the Star of David.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.03,1:16:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And I was going to ask you the significance\Nor the calibration of that.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.47,1:17:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what happened to her.\NShe was meditating, and she had said
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.60,1:17:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,there was two triangles, you know, in her mind.\NShe put her two triangles intercepting into her heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.21,1:17:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy.\NAnd then it said, as above, so below.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:09.64,1:17:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the words I was given.\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.48,1:17:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So she's wondering what the...\NLet me just calibrate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.60,1:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That was over 550, 600, 590.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:21.53,1:17:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,590, 580.\NIt was over 580.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.15,1:17:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It was over 580.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.35,1:17:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very good.\NIt's a nonverbal way of expressing something.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.18,1:17:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you want me to express it verbally.\NIf it was verbal, I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:37.14,1:17:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It wouldn't have come to you that way.\NIt would be verbal instead of nonverbal.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.22,1:17:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So if it's nonverbal, then it's not supposed to be verbal.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.14,1:17:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NVerbal anyways, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.50,1:18:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you verbalize\Nwith a nonverbal?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.47,1:18:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the dilemma.\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.23,1:18:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it is.\NI think that's why I have so much trouble once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:11.06,1:18:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NIt's like I understand it, but then for verbalizing it.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.67,1:18:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, that's true.\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.72,1:18:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.\NHi, Susan.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.30,1:18:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, Susan.\NHi, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.50,1:18:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.34,1:18:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to thank you both, and I wanted to thank you, Doc,\Nfor being my teacher.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.38,1:18:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And I just wanted to know if I could just touch your hand\Nand ask for a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.82,1:18:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What does she want now?\NA blessing.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.86,1:18:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Demanding, demanding, demanding.\NGod bless you, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:40.06,1:18:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.85,1:18:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.\NHello, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.47,1:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time since I've talked to you,\Nabout seven years since I last talked to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.97,1:19:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm very pleased and blessed to be in your presence,\Nand I want to thank you from the bottom of my heart
Dialogue: 0,1:19:07.86,1:19:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,for all of us for your work and your service and your love.\NAnd my question is regarding.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.52,1:19:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Pranayama.\NYou've repeatedly calibrated Pranayama at or below 200.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.47,1:19:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm a yoga teacher, and that's\None of the eight limbs of Patanjali's Yoga Sutras,
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.14,1:19:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,which you've calibrated, I believe, in the 700, 740.\NSo I'm confused.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.88,1:19:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you could give me some clarity about why Pranayama,\Nwhich is the fourth limb, is so low.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.94,1:19:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember what he's referring to.\NPranayama.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:54.03,1:19:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.\NWe have permission to calibrate Pranayama.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.97,1:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's that breathing exercise, you know.\NIt's a breathing exercise.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.85,1:20:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.\NIt calibrates over 500, calibrates over 495,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.56,1:20:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,calibrates over 350, 380, 340, 350, 350.\NA lot of exercises don't calibrate high.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.56,1:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYou know, standing on your head, for instance,
Dialogue: 0,1:20:23.81,1:20:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,probably doesn't calibrate very high.\NI'm sure there's yogas based on standing on your head.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.02,1:20:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There are, yeah.\NBecause yoga is based on every physical form, yes, or activity.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.81,1:20:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NSo you're saying it's actually 350 around there.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.31,1:20:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,About there.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.56,1:20:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's not bad.\NIt's about 300.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.40,1:20:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's the same as most Hatha yoga,\Nas you've calibrated it.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.14,1:20:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,But, you know, if you're talking about enlightenment,\Nthat isn't going to get you there at 350, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.72,1:21:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is.\NWhy are people attracted to the yogas anyway?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.50,1:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:07.14,1:21:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Of various reasons.\NYou mean the kind of we practice, like common in the West?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.82,1:21:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of what?\NThe yogas that are common in the West,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:16.09,1:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,like the physical yoga that most of them.\NOh, I see, those yogas, OK.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.77,1:21:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, see, he's doing physical yoga.\NOh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.90,1:21:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So that all calibrates at about three.\NUh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:26.97,1:21:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, 40, 350.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:28.97,1:21:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you were practicing.\NIt's in a positive direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:31.44,1:21:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NYou see, what impresses me about it,
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.09,1:21:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,about the yogas, is the intention behind it,\Nnot the yoga.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.31,1:21:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I enlightened now?\NIf you do that 1,000 times, now stop and do it 1,000 times
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.39,1:22:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,in the other direction.\NAm I enlightened now?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.15,1:22:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done it 1,000 times in both directions.\NGod feels sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.84,1:22:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,His angels say, there's a guy who's really willing down here.\NSo then God says, well, give him a pat.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.77,1:22:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, boom, boom.\NWow, wow, wow, wow, wow, wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:30.98,1:22:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It verges into, to my way of thinking, magical.\NIf I breathe this way and stand that way and eat this
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.47,1:22:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and eat that, to my way of thinking,\Nit's you're trying to employ the magical.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:45.97,1:22:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.\NOK.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.90,1:22:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is correct.\NYou're employing the magical.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.77,1:22:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're employing magic.\NSo a lot of what goes as yoga is just magical thinking.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.94,1:23:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoo-ha, hoo-ha, boo-hoo, hoo-hoo, yee-hee, ha-ha, hoo-hoo, ha-ha.\NAm I any closer to God than I was?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.60,1:23:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But all action.\NGod's giggling all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.28,1:23:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All action dedicated to God then would take on the level 540.\NYeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.28,1:23:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I dedicate.\NIf you're doing it out of devotion to God, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:22.65,1:23:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it.\NOK.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.46,1:23:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it.\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:27.01,1:23:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're doing it out of devotion to God.\NAnd then there's the desire for enlightenment.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.71,1:23:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And you really have to contemplate\Nwhat is the correlation between those two things,
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.15,1:23:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,surrender to God and reaching enlightenment.\NIf you surrender to God, you give up
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.05,1:24:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,working towards enlightenment because now it's up to God.\NYou understand the conflict you get into?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:05.03,1:24:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NBut in resolving the conflict, you find your way.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.53,1:24:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you don't need to worry.\NSo sacrifice is giving it up to God is always the ultimate path.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.85,1:24:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,God feels sorry for you in the end.\NYeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:20.09,1:24:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NI had another question for my friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.89,1:24:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,She's very shy, so she didn't come up here.\NBut she wanted to know, is it healthy for she raises dogs
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.72,1:24:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,to let them sleep with you in your bed?\NIs that?
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.77,1:24:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it helping to allow dogs to sleep in your bed?\NSure.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.44,1:25:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,If you love the dogs, yes.\NIf you hate the dogs, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.92,1:25:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I think loving pets gets you closer to God.\NLoving pets gets you closer to God, resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.89,1:25:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NYou love your kitties and your doggies and your bunnies
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.50,1:25:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and birdies and chickens and what else we got?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.35,1:25:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't see the end.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.77,1:25:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see the end.\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:26.40,1:25:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,OK.\NWhat's the bird that talks?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.90,1:25:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tucks, what, broccoli?\NBroccoli, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.94,1:25:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you call him?\NWhat is he, he's a?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.43,1:25:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,African grey.\NAfrican grey parrot, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.22,1:25:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,She.\NShe's an African grey parrot.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.97,1:25:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,She's an African grey parrot.\NWe have an African grey parrot that is a real knock out.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.38,1:25:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NSays the funniest things unexpectedly.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.69,1:26:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I think, you know, loving all of God's creations\Nbecause I love the elephants, too, and I love the tigers.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.43,1:26:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're all just stunningly beautiful.\NOne more thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:08.76,1:26:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I am with a group, SCA, Self-Centered Anonymous,\Nthat is, you may have heard of them.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.92,1:26:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We meet, well, anyway, they follow your teachings.\NWe're all followers of you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.42,1:26:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I told them I was coming today,\Nand they wanted to know if you might have something to say to the group.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:26.84,1:26:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What group?\NThis group he belongs to.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.03,1:26:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a 12-step group.\NIt's like a 12-step group.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.73,1:26:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,12-step group.\NBased on self-centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.61,1:26:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Based on what?\NSelf-centeredness.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.14,1:26:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you want to become more self-centered?\NNo, they're trying not to.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.42,1:26:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NYou want to stop being self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.73,1:26:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?\NThat's pretty self-centered, to want to stop being self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.27,1:27:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,The trouble is you're not being self-centered enough.\NIf you do it with great intensity, nonstop,
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.86,1:27:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,then you'll get relieved of it, because you can't.\NI know what you're asking, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.52,1:27:24.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's subtle.\NIt's subtle.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:24.89,1:27:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How to let things be without projecting one's own willfulness into it.\NHow to let the world be as it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.56,1:27:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,How to let yourself be as you are.\NHow to let others be as they are.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.77,1:27:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're really asking how to surrender to God, yes.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.31,1:27:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And if...\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:47.93,1:27:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.02,1:27:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.14,1:27:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.30,1:27:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.42,1:27:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.56,1:27:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NMm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:48.60,1:27:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're self-centered is where you're at with it,\Nthen you surrender to God that you're self-centered.
Dialogue: 0,1:27:57.61,1:27:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're self-centered.\NBig deal.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.86,1:28:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a sin?\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:06.18,1:28:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you trying to escape it?\NI don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:12.50,1:28:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the desire to be selfless.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:14.89,1:28:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.\NAnd what is it that desires to be selfless?
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.92,1:28:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The will, you know?\NIt's just that you've given it direction.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.56,1:28:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're in a good space.\NYou're in a good pathway.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.43,1:28:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in a good pathway.\NWonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:35.92,1:28:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Doctor.\NDon't be impatient.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.85,1:28:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NIt only takes 40, 50 lifetimes.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.15,1:28:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Here comes the clinking, yeah.\NYou're fine, but...
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.39,1:28:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,However, it can also be accomplished in 30 seconds.\NBy the time you reach the edge of the stage, you will be enlightened.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:48.09,1:28:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You have now just entered the world of evolution.\NThe end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:57.11,1:28:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:28:59.11,1:29:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:01.11,1:29:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.11,1:29:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThe time and moment of his enlightenment is now recorded for all of posterity.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:25.77,1:29:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It is said that kinesiology test can only be applied to past or present.\NHowever, if there is no such thing as past, present, or future, why kinesiology cannot
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.97,1:29:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,be applied to future, or what we define as future, if there is no such thing as future\Nexists.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.97,1:29:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what she's saying so far.\NIt's a riddle.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:51.97,1:29:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Riddle, riddles?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.06,1:29:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a riddle to me.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:56.06,1:30:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She says that if there's no such thing as past, present, and future, then how can you\Ncall it past, present, and future?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:04.21,1:30:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody said there is no such thing.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:06.21,1:30:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NNobody said there is no such thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.68,1:30:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said there's no such thing?\NI think it's in your books.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:10.68,1:30:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:12.68,1:30:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think we said there was no such thing.\NWe just said that.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:14.68,1:30:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NMaybe it's a different verbalization.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:16.68,1:30:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a way of looking at things.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:18.68,1:30:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Arbitrary way of looking at things.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:21.39,1:30:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is the question?\NIf there's no such thing as past, present, and future, then what?
Dialogue: 0,1:30:23.39,1:30:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, kinesiology test can only be applied.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:25.39,1:30:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NThat's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:27.39,1:30:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot, we can look at the past because we test the past all the time.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:29.39,1:30:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't look at the future.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:31.39,1:30:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the future has no existence.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.39,1:30:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NThat's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:35.39,1:30:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot, we can look at the past.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:37.39,1:30:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because we test the past all the time.\NBut we can't look at the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:39.39,1:30:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NBecause the future has no existence.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.39,1:30:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because the future does not exist.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.39,1:30:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can look at the present, and we can look at the past.\NOr the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:45.39,1:30:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NBut we can't look at the future.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:47.39,1:30:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NI will reread your chapter again.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.39,1:30:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NFor clarification.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:51.39,1:30:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.39,1:30:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't.\NMaybe I just, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:55.39,1:30:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NBecause anything that's in the past, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:57.39,1:30:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NWell, it's a.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.39,1:31:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NBut the, but anything that's in the future, you can't see because it hasn't materialized
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.39,1:31:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,yet.\NAnd there's free will in there, and it changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:03.39,1:31:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't look at the future.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:05.39,1:31:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NBut we can't look at the past.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:07.39,1:31:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Because anything that's in the future, you can't see because it hasn't materialized yet.\NAnd there's free will in there, and it changes.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:09.39,1:31:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So you can't predict the future.\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.39,1:31:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I can't say, invest in this.\NThis is going to be a good investment because.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:13.39,1:31:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NAnd I'm going to make X amount of dollars.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:15.39,1:31:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do that with it.\NHmm.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:17.39,1:31:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Life would be very boring if you could.\NI just don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.39,1:31:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, control and predict the future.\NNo.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:21.39,1:31:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not.\NIt just.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:23.39,1:31:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be like reading your own mail all day.\NRight.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:25.39,1:31:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I.\NIt just said.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:27.39,1:31:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,At a certain point.\NLike you.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:29.39,1:31:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know.\NAnyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:31.39,1:31:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hoffman.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.39,1:31:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Hoffman.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:35.39,1:31:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:37.39,1:31:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:39.39,1:31:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:41.39,1:31:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.39,1:31:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.39,1:31:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:47.39,1:31:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.\NDr. Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:49.39,1:31:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You.\NIn your book, Truth Versus Falsehood, you calibrated Ramesh Balsekar at 760.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:51.39,1:31:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I never heard afterwards anything you'd.\NWell, we didn't read any books about him, did we?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:53.39,1:31:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\NWhy would you hear about him?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:55.39,1:31:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't about him, but.\NWhy would you hear about him?
Dialogue: 0,1:31:57.39,1:32:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because he was involved into kind of scanning.\NAnd he was.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:00.22,1:32:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was.\NHe was.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:02.22,1:32:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He was.\NHe was killed in the war.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:06.22,1:32:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There were scandals.\NThere were scandals and lawsuits.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:08.22,1:32:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about all that.\NI mean, either.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:10.22,1:32:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I wrote, you know, it's like if you wrote an encyclopedia in 1956.\NThat doesn't mean it's supposed to include things that didn't happen until 1980.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:19.60,1:32:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're not being rational in the expectation.\NMay ask question.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:24.42,1:32:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If at the end of his life, he passed away a couple of years ago, if he calibrated at\N760 as, no.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:32.35,1:32:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?\NIt's an elastic.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:35.69,1:32:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's.\NWhat is that?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:37.88,1:32:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Some people fall.\NSome people fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:39.97,1:32:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, and that's my question.\NSpiritual teachers fall all the time.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:43.72,1:32:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:45.03,1:32:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, fame, sex.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.00,1:32:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That takes care of all of them.\NThat's what rules the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:50.14,1:32:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Money, fame, and sex.\NAnd their dream is to have all three at one,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:55.65,1:32:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,become famous,\Nand have a rich and powerful, seductive girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.61,1:33:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,who just jumps in bed with you.\NThat's going back to kindergarten.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:05.63,1:33:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it started from the beginning again.\NSo, okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:10.53,1:33:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So, no, he didn't.\NWe won't calibrate him, but he fell after.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.97,1:33:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's my...\NYeah, but at the time we calibrated him,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.89,1:33:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he was at that.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:19.35,1:33:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:21.26,1:33:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's been 10 years ago, you know, or more.\NMany, the majority, I would think, grew his fall.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:29.10,1:33:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It was very high, 760,\Nand I kind of attracted to his books.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.47,1:33:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's straight and plain.\NWell, when he...
Dialogue: 0,1:33:37.72,1:33:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes...\NWhen they're writing books and they're doing the work,
Dialogue: 0,1:33:43.22,1:33:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,their calibrations are very attractive,\Nbut, you know, the work sometimes is not the man.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:51.02,1:33:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.\NYeah, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:53.56,1:33:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, thanks for listening.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.23,1:34:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your time, Karen.\NI don't keep up with the current scandal
Dialogue: 0,1:34:03.96,1:34:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,of various former teachers.\NRight, but that was the one that...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:07.96,1:34:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.\NOkay, we'll take...
Dialogue: 0,1:34:11.73,1:34:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When do we...\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:13.15,1:34:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my thing's off.\NSorry, you fell from grace.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.56,1:34:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:21.22,1:34:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My watch is...\NSomething's wrong with my watch.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:25.23,1:34:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:26.22,1:34:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,My question has to do with overcoming karma.\NI have Renard's.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.96,1:34:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where your hands get really cold\Nand the fingers will turn white in the cold.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:38.42,1:34:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And through kinesiology,\Nit was identified as a past life expression of ancient karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:45.77,1:34:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm wondering if the undoing of that\Nis through prayer,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.00,1:34:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and also you answered another question about karma\Nand undoing bad karma with good karma.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:58.89,1:35:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And the thought that immediately came to my mind\Nwas for me to volunteer at a hospice because I...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.23,1:35:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That would be good, yes.\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:10.10,1:35:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that would be good.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:13.21,1:35:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's talking about what I used to have.\NI forget the name of it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:19.05,1:35:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Renard.\NRenard syndrome?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.63,1:35:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:22.14,1:35:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Renos.\NYes, Renos disease, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:24.77,1:35:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NNo, that would be perfect, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.64,1:35:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:30.93,1:35:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NI'm going to have a picture.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:32.77,1:35:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:41.38,1:35:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I used to have to wear gloves in the...\NI had to wear gloves even in the house.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:48.94,1:35:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And I related it one time\Ngoing to a Chinese restaurant
Dialogue: 0,1:35:54.47,1:36:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and eating with chopsticks with my gloves on.\NGood morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.64,1:36:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.\NGood morning.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:04.27,1:36:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You previously stated that you can only go as high\Nas you have gone low.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.78,1:36:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you speak and say more about that?\NWell, it's a saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:16.38,1:36:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not...\NIt's hypothetically true.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:22.52,1:36:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But it can vary from individual to individual.\NIf a person hits the depths, they despair.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:34.63,1:36:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,But if you tell them there's a benefit to that,\Na benefit,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.19,1:36:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,you've looked at things\Nthat you otherwise couldn't have handled
Dialogue: 0,1:36:42.96,1:36:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or couldn't have looked at,\Nand you've now earned the right to transcend them.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:49.72,1:36:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's like a karmic benefit\Nto have looked at the darkest,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.07,1:37:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,been through the worst,\Nand you've still maintained your allegiance to God
Dialogue: 0,1:37:01.32,1:37:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,and truth and love and divinity.\NThen you've earned the karmic right to transcend it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:07.93,1:37:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's sort of a saying.\NYou can only be as high as...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:11.72,1:37:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You once were low.\NAnd it's karmically often true.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.32,1:37:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's karmically often true.\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.77,1:37:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?\NIt's an individual matter.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:23.84,1:37:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In an individual matter, yeah.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:30.51,1:37:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this will be the last question.\NYes, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.30,1:37:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:38.77,1:37:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Boo.\NBoo.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:44.15,1:37:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You got one last cookie you want to go?\NOne last quick question or not?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:48.19,1:37:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.\NDo we...
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.73,1:37:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to do a closing.\NI'd like to have a prayer sent.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:55.93,1:37:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NI'd like us all to pray for Japan
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.57,1:38:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people that are suffering\Nand have passed away.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:03.39,1:38:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's do that.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.77,1:38:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can all join together\Nto try to offset what's going on currently in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.52,1:38:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you'll have to lead the prayer on this\Nbecause it was your thought.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:22.44,1:38:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have the thought.\NWhat does he want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:32.89,1:38:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is the mic?\NIt's on you.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.32,1:38:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have one.\NWell, here.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:36.56,1:38:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You take it.\NYou're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.76,1:38:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No flies on me.\NHi.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.22,1:38:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I on?\NOh, there you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.92,1:38:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I want all of us to do a silent prayer\Nfor the people in Japan that are suffering.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.93,1:38:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We recently had a lovely lady from our group\Nthat has crossed over.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:00.02,1:39:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So if everyone could say a prayer\Nfor these people that are now making the transition,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:06.69,1:39:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we appreciate it very much.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.72,1:39:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,If we could just do a silent prayer for those people,\Nit would be very nice.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.72,1:39:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We pray for thy love and forgiveness\Nto heal the sorrow and the pain and the suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:39:29.89,1:39:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,of people who are caught in that catastrophe\Nand that their suffering may lead to serve thee.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.68,1:39:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Lord, amen.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.98,1:39:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you want to go ahead and bless everyone that's here.\NWe're so grateful for all of you to come.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.14,1:39:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you have come quite a long distance to be with us.\NAnd we appreciate it so much
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.09,1:40:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,because without you, the work would be nothing.\NAnd we are so appreciative of all of you
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.14,1:40:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,showing up for the events.\NIt touches both of our hearts very deeply.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:07.77,1:40:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We thank thee, O Lord, for thy divine blessing\Nupon this group of people here assembled this day.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.76,1:40:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We give thanks for thy presence, O Lord.\NAmen.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.27,1:40:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And now we hug each other and bless each other.\NThat's the part I always like.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:36.01,1:40:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the best part of the whole show.\NBig hug and God love you.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:43.72,1:40:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at these beautiful flowers on top of it.\NSomebody sent us these gorgeous flowers.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.97,1:40:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My God, they're beautiful.\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.52,1:41:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Lidart.\NHave I got a mic on now?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.89,1:41:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.\NWhere is the mic?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:14.27,1:41:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.\NI have a microphone attached to my cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.00,1:41:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you know about that?\NI didn't know I had a microphone attached to my cheek.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.85,1:41:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead and rush this little microphone.\NIt's God's microphone.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:35.22,1:41:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, God.\NWe've had a lovely day.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.64,1:41:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lovely day to be here again with you this day.\NYour love is a blessing to the world.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:56.14,1:42:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When the love of this group is sent\Nto the people in trouble in Japan,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:01.50,1:42:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,it actually has,\Nit actually has an effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.02,1:42:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It actually has a literal,\Nreal effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.56,1:42:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless them.\NOh, Lord.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.56,1:42:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Amen.\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.56,1:42:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me hear it.\NThat had a literal,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:15.80,1:42:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,physical effect.\NWow.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.80,1:42:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.\NThank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.92,1:42:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this microphone still on?\NOh, I just love that old doc.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.89,1:42:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's also a sweetheart.\NOh, I just love him.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:58.89,1:43:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Docky Dock.\NGive me a kiss, baby.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:01.40,1:43:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.65,1:43:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:07.75,1:43:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:10.28,1:43:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.60,1:43:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
